Subject: [PATCH] feat: Fix loading flash, add password management, fix sidebar
 scroll

- DataContext: show loading spinner while API data loads (fixes flash of old content)
- Server: add /api/admin/login and /api/admin/password endpoints with JSON file storage
- AdminLayout: auth now checks password via server API instead of hardcoded check
- AdminLayout: added password change UI in Site Settings section
- AdminLayout: fixed sidebar nav scroll (added overflow-y-auto)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
